snippet.title: Super Mario 64: Last Impact V1.2 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This romhack aims to be more than just an SM64 DLC and creates many new mechanics to make for an entirely new Mario experience.
For more fangames, subscribe to this channel! https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1

Music is "Secret Desk" by Dotstarmoney, a custom composition for this romhack.
Changelog:
https://pastebin.com/RZSfyvJF

Download:
https://mega.nz/#!GCIziaqJ!SzBkng0w0ktovmZotXgr6X_ATkN0NX9uqtfX5Fy6uTQ

My recommended emulator:
http://www.emulator-zone.com/download.php/emulators/n64/project64/project64_1.6.exe
(any other one should work too though)
